  "texts": [
    "• OpenAI API Integration: The OpenAI API was utilized to generate interconnected triplets from the AI responses.",
    "Each triplet was formatted as \"Entity1:Relationship:Entity2\".",
    "• Triplet Aggregation: A function was designed to concatenate responses from two different datasets for the same questions and create a set of interconnected triplets.",
    "• Knowledge Graph Assembly: The triplets were then used to construct directed graphs using the NetworkX library.",
    "Each graph represents the knowledge encapsulated in the AI responses, with nodes for entities and directed edges for relationships."
  ],
